<#assign dashboardContent>
  <div class = "row well" >
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <h3>Draw up a play</h3>
      <p>
        Whether before, during, or after a game, you will find play-maker 
        is a step up on your typical whiteboard 
        with the ability to create, animate, and save plays.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <h3>Analyze line-ups</h3>
      <p>
        With various metrics, you can now ensure you're putting your best foot forward. Optimize your lineups for the best court coverage and recent performance. 
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <h3>Start a Game</h3>
      <p>
        Throw us right into the action! Live-stats, play-maker, and whiteboard at your disposal allow you to focus on coaching your team.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <h3>Log real-time stats</h3>
      <p>
        With each game, the app will store every stat ever logged by your managers. Investigate players, teams, or games through graphs, heat-maps, and boxscores. 
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row well">
    <div class="col-md-12 big-button">
      <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" id="start-game">Start a Game!</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <script src="/js/dashboard_no_game.js"></script>
</#assign>
<#include "dashboard.ftl">
